21. Rf7 Qd6 22. Qf5?? { Understandably threatening e7+ next move, but Black can prevent it easily with Re8. As a result, Black is up a rook and will win the game. } (22. e7+!! { The most forcing continuation! } 22... Kd7 (22... Ke8 23. Rh7+) 23. Qf5+ Kc7 24. e8=N+ Kb6 25. Nxd6 { White wins in all continuations }) 22... Re8 *


